| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7107 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3eb4116a-0b69-5e59-8721-4d2bfdd3b374"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
